ress.";i:66;s:56:"When it is closed there is a knock option on long press.";i:67;s:102:"If you live near a coastal region your garage door can likely rust due to humidity present in the air.";i:68;s:45:"Repeat this until the surface is shiny again.";i:69;s:43:"Secure The Garage Door And Remove The Rust.";i:70;s:52:"Go inside of the garage and close and lock the door.";i:71;s:80:"Set up a step ladder near the doors interior so that you can access the springs.";i:72;s:79:"The springs will look like long cylinders that are placed horizontally towards.";i:73;s:87:"You can easily remove doors you own if it is woodensheet metalarmored single or double.";i:74;s:98:"Simply tap the E key to open the door mouse over the lock hold the E key select the unlock option.";i:75;s:80:"Once the lock turns green hold the E key again to choose the pickup lock option.";i:76;s:84:"Once thats done hold the E key anywhere on the door and youll see the pickup prompt.";}}